    public abstract class AbstractControlledDataInboundPort
extends fr.upmc.components.ports.AbstractDataInboundPort
implements ControlledDataOfferedI.ControlledPullI
    The class AbstractControlledDataInboundPort defines an abstract controlled inbound port where the push interface adds control method to start and stop the pushing.
